Aker Floating Production ( OSE : AKFP ) is a Norwegian Floating Production Storage and Offloading vessel operator . The company is part of the Aker Group with Aker ASA owning 44.27 % of the company . It is also listed on Oslo Stock Exchange . The company was founded March 14 2006 . It has pruchased three oil tankers for conversion to FPSO vessels , and the first vessel will be delivered in the third quarter of 2007 . The company plans to have four FPSOs in operation by 2009 . 